  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Provision of a multicurrency senior loan of up to EUR 125 million equivalent in  support of Grupa Azoty Polyolefins S.A. (&quot;PDHP&quot;), a subsidiary of Grupa Azoty  Zaklady Chemiczne &quot;Police&quot; S.A. (&quot;GA Police&quot;) and Grupa Azoty S.A. (&quot;Grupa  Azoty&quot;), which is considering the construction and operation of an  integrated propane dehydrogenation unit (&quot;PDH&quot;) and polypropylene unit  (&quot;PP&quot;) to manufacture propylene and polypropylene. The facilities will be  located in the town of Police, adjacent to the existing facilities of GA Police  and will have access to its utilities and infrastructure.</narrative>
